                            <comment id="15003500" author="bcg" created="Fri, 13 Nov 2015 03:32:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I didn&apos;t add any actual tests for this, other than a namespace declaration in the TestThrift.thrift file that should fail if the compiler does not have this change included.  I&apos;d be glad to add better test(s) but I&apos;m not familiar with how to do that within the Thrift build framework, as the tests in the tests/ folder seem mostly focused on testing protocol and transport implementations.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also I&apos;ve not written much C++ for quite a while, so please check for style and correctness, and please do not hesitate to point any problems with my style or incorrectness.&lt;/p&gt;

